58
00:04:18,664 --> 00:04:20,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Ryosuke Takahashi.</b></font>

59
00:04:20,774 --> 00:04:22,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm a member of the Red Suns.</b></font>

60
00:04:22,534 --> 00:04:23,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know.</b></font>

61
00:04:23,844 --> 00:04:25,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm Takeshi Nakazato.</b></font>

62
00:04:25,574 --> 00:04:28,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I belong to a team at Mt. Myogi
called the Night Kids.</b></font>

63
00:04:28,744 --> 00:04:31,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takeshi Nakazato of the Night Kids...?</b></font>

64
00:04:31,414 --> 00:04:34,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you the fastest street racer
on Mt. Myogi's downhill?</b></font>

65
00:04:34,414 --> 00:04:39,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm honored to be recognized by
the superstar, Ryosuke Takahashi.</b></font>

66
00:04:39,384 --> 00:04:43,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I've heard Nakazato of the Night Kids</b></font>

67
00:04:43,524 --> 00:04:47,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is driving an S13, if I remember correctly...</b></font>

68
00:04:50,134 --> 00:04:51,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't matter...</b></font>

69
00:04:51,734 --> 00:04:54,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So what is a street racer
from Myogi doing at Akina?</b></font>

70
00:04:54,734 --> 00:04:57,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hang on a minute. Let's not talk about me.</b></font>

71
00:04:57,474 --> 00:05:00,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You belong to Akagi, don't you?</b></font>

72
00:05:00,044 --> 00:05:03,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Didn't we come here for the same reason?</b></font>

73
00:05:03,644 --> 00:05:09,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanted to meet the Eight-Six I saw yesterday.</b></font>

74
00:05:09,654 --> 00:05:13,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The one using the R32
tries to bite the Eight-Six?</b></font>

75
00:05:13,854 --> 00:05:17,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With the R32, which is
tuned for 380 horsepower...</b></font>

76
00:05:17,224 --> 00:05:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

77
00:05:18,564 --> 00:05:20,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can see it easily</b></font>

78
00:05:20,194 --> 00:05:21,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by looking at the exhaust</b></font>

79
00:05:21,994 --> 00:05:23,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and its power on the straightaways.</b></font>

80
00:05:23,834 --> 00:05:26,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the result is obvious.</b></font>

81
00:05:26,564 --> 00:05:29,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the uphill, the Eight-Six
is no match for the R32.</b></font>

82
00:05:29,834 --> 00:05:33,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the downhill, there is no way</b></font>

83
00:05:33,104 --> 00:05:35,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>your R32 can beat the Eight-Six.</b></font>

84
00:05:35,244 --> 00:05:36,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did you say?</b></font>

85
00:05:36,844 --> 00:05:40,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you saying my R32 will lose
to the Eight-Six on the downhill?!</b></font>

86
00:05:40,244 --> 00:05:45,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't take it personally.
I'm just saying what I think.</b></font>

87
00:05:45,624 --> 00:05:47,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't have much nerve.</b></font>

88
00:05:47,794 --> 00:05:49,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even though your brother lost,</b></font>

89
00:05:49,194 --> 00:05:51,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>there's no need to be so intimidated.</b></font>

90
00:05:51,694 --> 00:05:53,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just an Eight-Six.</b></font>

91
00:05:53,864 --> 00:05:56,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you race against it, you'll see.</b></font>

92
00:05:56,634 --> 00:05:58,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm the only one who can beat him.</b></font>

93
00:05:58,934 --> 00:06:00,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't joke with me.</b></font>

94
00:06:00,374 --> 00:06:03,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've already said it, and now
I can't walk away no matter what.</b></font>

95
00:06:03,004 --> 00:06:06,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll beat the Eight-Six and
make you eat your words.</b></font>

96
00:06:06,244 --> 00:06:08,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can be arrogant for now.</b></font>

97
00:06:08,974 --> 00:06:12,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget that I am Nakazato from Myogi!</b></font>

98
00:06:12,484 --> 00:06:13,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm telling you now</b></font>

99
00:06:13,754 --> 00:06:16,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that the rotary is not a match for this R32!</b></font>

100
00:06:30,194 --> 00:06:34,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...driving an S13, if I remember correctly...</i></b></font>

101
00:06:34,434 --> 00:06:38,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's right... since that time, I have changed.</i></b></font>

102
00:06:53,854 --> 00:06:56,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Damn! I can't pass it!</i></b></font>

103
00:06:56,754 --> 00:06:57,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if I get close in the corner,</i></b></font>

104
00:06:57,864 --> 00:06:59,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>he pulls away in the straightaway...</i></b></font>

105
00:06:59,394 --> 00:07:02,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have better technique as a racer!</i></b></font>

106
00:07:02,634 --> 00:07:04,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Crap! How could I lose?!</i></b></font>

107
00:07:29,754 --> 00:07:31,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With this S13, I can't beat an R32,</i></b></font>

108
00:07:31,994 --> 00:07:34,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>no matter what I do...</i></b></font>

109
00:07:34,334 --> 00:07:37,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I, who was called the fastest</i>
<i>street racer on Mt. Myogi's downhill,</i></b></font>

110
00:07:37,934 --> 00:07:41,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>lost to an R32, which can't even do a drift...!</i></b></font>

111
00:07:42,104 --> 00:07:44,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All cars have their limits.</i></b></font>

112
00:07:44,544 --> 00:07:46,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No matter how excellent</i>
<i>the driver's technique is,</i></b></font>

113
00:07:46,704 --> 00:07:49,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>you can't drive beyond the car's limit.</i></b></font>

114
00:07:49,614 --> 00:07:52,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even that Eight-Six...!</i></b></font>

115
00:08:00,184 --> 00:08:02,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good morning!</b></font>

116
00:08:02,354 --> 00:08:03,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey!</b></font>

117
00:08:03,554 --> 00:08:05,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here, Iketani!</b></font>

118
00:08:05,324 --> 00:08:07,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that?</b></font>

119
00:08:07,024 --> 00:08:08,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fried tofu.</b></font>

120
00:08:08,534 --> 00:08:10,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's left over from yesterday.</b></font>

121
00:08:10,294 --> 00:08:12,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My father told me to bring it to you.</b></font>

122
00:08:12,304 --> 00:08:13,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, really?</b></font>

123
00:08:13,464 --> 00:08:15,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll put it in the refrigerator.</b></font>

124
00:08:15,634 --> 00:08:18,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow... I'm surprised he thought of me...</b></font>

125
00:08:20,974 --> 00:08:22,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--By the way, Takumi...
--Yeah...?</b></font>

126
00:08:22,874 --> 00:08:24,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it true that you've been delivering tofu</b></font>

127
00:08:24,714 --> 00:08:26,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to Lake Akina for the last five years?</b></font>

128
00:08:26,814 --> 00:08:28,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

129
00:08:28,554 --> 00:08:33,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought we were friends.
Why didn't you tell me?</b></font>

130
00:08:33,324 --> 00:08:37,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because if I talked about it,
we could have gotten into trouble...</b></font>

131
00:08:37,924 --> 00:08:39,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well... I guess so...</b></font>

132
00:08:39,994 --> 00:08:41,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five years ago,</b></font>

133
00:08:41,834 --> 00:08:45,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we were just starting junior high...</b></font>

134
00:08:48,074 --> 00:08:51,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've driven much longer than I have.</b></font>

135
00:08:51,544 --> 00:08:53,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since junior high,
you've been driving every day,</b></font>

136
00:08:53,604 --> 00:08:57,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even in the snow and rain, on Mt. Akina.</b></font>

137
00:08:57,544 --> 00:09:00,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's early in the morning.
So I don't see anyone...</b></font>

138
00:09:00,784 --> 00:09:05,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, not that! Those corners!
Weren't you scared?</b></font>

139
00:09:05,284 --> 00:09:08,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well... in the beginning, I was scared.</b></font>

140
00:09:08,854 --> 00:09:12,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the fear was completely
gone within six months.</b></font>

141
00:09:12,464 --> 00:09:15,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I accelerate, the tires slip naturally.</b></font>

142
00:09:15,834 --> 00:09:17,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So it took another half year</b></font>

143
00:09:17,304 --> 00:09:20,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>until I could slip and control them as I wanted.</b></font>

144
00:09:20,304 --> 00:09:21,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That means...</b></font>

145
00:09:21,704 --> 00:09:24,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...you mastered the downhill in a year.</b></font>

146
00:09:24,344 --> 00:09:25,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you do it every day,</b></font>

147
00:09:25,704 --> 00:09:28,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>your nervousness about
slipping disappears quickly.</b></font>

148
00:09:28,874 --> 00:09:30,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had nothing to do,</b></font>

149
00:09:30,644 --> 00:09:34,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I started to see how close
I could get to the guardrails...</b></font>

150
00:09:34,054 --> 00:09:35,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Would a normal person do
something that dangerous?!</b></font>

151
00:09:35,814 --> 00:09:38,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never thought it was dangerous.</b></font>

152
00:09:38,554 --> 00:09:42,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I'm at my best, I can
get as close as about 1 cm.</b></font>

153
00:09:42,894 --> 00:09:45,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One... one centimeter?!</b></font>

154
00:09:45,564 --> 00:09:48,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unless I find fun stuff to do like that,</b></font>

155
00:09:48,394 --> 00:09:49,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's pretty boring</b></font>

156
00:09:49,894 --> 00:09:52,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>helping with my father's business.</b></font>

157
00:09:52,264 --> 00:09:57,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I've never thought I
wanted to improve as a driver...</b></font>

158
00:09:57,004 --> 00:09:58,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I would get impatient,</b></font>

159
00:09:58,744 --> 00:10:00,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and would want to get home faster.</b></font>

160
00:10:00,404 --> 00:10:02,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So when I don't have tofu on the way back,</b></font>

161
00:10:02,014 --> 00:10:04,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I go as fast as I can.</b></font>

162
00:10:04,914 --> 00:10:08,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Takumi... can I ask you a question?
--Yes...</b></font>

163
00:10:08,284 --> 00:10:11,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How do you drive when
you have tofu in the car?</b></font>

164
00:10:11,354 --> 00:10:13,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you go too fast, you'll
damage the tofu, won't you?</b></font>

165
00:10:13,724 --> 00:10:16,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't go very fast on the uphill...</b></font>

166
00:10:19,124 --> 00:10:21,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My father puts water in a paper cup</b></font>

167
00:10:21,234 --> 00:10:23,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and puts it in the cup holder.</b></font>

168
00:10:23,764 --> 00:10:25,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I can drive without spilling the water,</b></font>

169
00:10:25,604 --> 00:10:28,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he says I won't damage
the tofu, even if I'm going fast.</b></font>

170
00:10:30,134 --> 00:10:33,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the beginning, I found it to be very difficult.</b></font>

171
00:10:33,544 --> 00:10:36,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even when I drove slowly, it spilled all over...</b></font>

172
00:10:36,544 --> 00:10:38,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I would think so...</b></font>

173
00:10:38,144 --> 00:10:40,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Brake, steering wheel, shifting, gas pedal...</b></font>

174
00:10:40,714 --> 00:10:44,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If even one of them is a
little rough, the water spills.</b></font>

175
00:10:44,884 --> 00:10:48,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My father often says to roll
the water in the paper cup.</b></font>

176
00:10:48,624 --> 00:10:50,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Roll the water in the cup?</b></font>

177
00:10:50,894 --> 00:10:53,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I suppose it's the surface tension...</b></font>

178
00:10:53,224 --> 00:10:54,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The water's surface tension</b></font>

179
00:10:54,794 --> 00:10:58,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>makes it roll around the rim of the cup.</b></font>

180
00:10:58,904 --> 00:11:01,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At each corner,</b></font>

181
00:11:01,004 --> 00:11:04,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I roll the water to the edge
of the rim as I drive up the hill.</b></font>

182
00:11:06,004 --> 00:11:07,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It took me a long time</b></font>

183
00:11:07,744 --> 00:11:11,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to be able to drift without spilling the water.</b></font>

184
00:11:11,084 --> 00:11:13,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drift without spilling the water?!</b></font>

185
00:11:13,114 --> 00:11:14,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you really do that?!</b></font>

186
00:11:17,084 --> 00:11:20,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't lie! You're just joking, right?!</b></font>

187
00:11:20,284 --> 00:11:25,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The primary point in controlling
a car is the center of balance.</b></font>

188
00:11:25,194 --> 00:11:29,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Drift King, Keiichi Tsuchiya,
also says so in the video...</b></font>

189
00:11:29,034 --> 00:11:31,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In order to drive without spilling
the water in the paper cup,</b></font>

190
00:11:31,864 --> 00:11:36,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you have to master the car's center of balance.</b></font>

191
00:11:36,804 --> 00:11:39,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not to mention drifting...</b></font>

192
00:11:39,204 --> 00:11:41,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's impossible to do that!</b></font>

193
00:11:41,614 --> 00:11:44,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not lying!</b></font>

194
00:11:44,044 --> 00:11:45,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just because you beat Keisuke Takahashi...</b></font>

195
00:11:45,584 --> 00:11:48,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're carrying it way too far! I know better...</b></font>

196
00:11:48,654 --> 00:11:50,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Oh, a customer.
--Oops...</b></font>

197
00:11:50,724 --> 00:11:52,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome!</b></font>

198
00:11:52,424 --> 00:11:54,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fill it up with high octane? Yes, sir!</b></font>

199
00:11:56,754 --> 00:11:58,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Amazing, Bunta...</i></b></font>

200
00:11:58,224 --> 00:12:01,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His technique is way above</i>
<i>just a regular mountain racer...</i></b></font>

201
00:12:01,734 --> 00:12:04,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

202
00:12:07,774 --> 00:12:09,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! I have a favor to ask.</b></font>

203
00:12:09,674 --> 00:12:11,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you let me ride next to you</b></font>

204
00:12:11,344 --> 00:12:14,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when you do the downhill at Akina?</b></font>

205
00:12:26,124 --> 00:12:29,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

206
00:12:27,354 --> 00:12:29,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You want to use the car?</b></font>

207
00:12:29,354 --> 00:12:31,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this time of the day?</b></font>

208
00:12:31,124 --> 00:12:32,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, well, I didn't think you'd let me.</b></font>

209
00:12:32,894 --> 00:12:35,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all right. It's not a big deal.</b></font>

210
00:12:35,094 --> 00:12:36,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't mind.</b></font>

211
00:12:36,794 --> 00:12:38,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure?</b></font>

212
00:12:38,404 --> 00:12:41,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you need the car for anything?</b></font>

213
00:12:41,374 --> 00:12:44,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like a meeting at the Chamber
of Commerce or something?</b></font>

214
00:12:44,074 --> 00:12:46,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd better think a little bit.</b></font>

215
00:12:46,544 --> 00:12:47,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?</b></font>

216
00:12:47,814 --> 00:12:50,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You sound like you'll be in trouble
if I don't have to use the car.</b></font>

217
00:12:50,544 --> 00:12:53,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, no... I didn't mean that...</b></font>

218
00:12:53,544 --> 00:12:55,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then take the car.</b></font>

219
00:12:55,114 --> 00:12:59,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But in return, you need to
pick me up at my meeting.</b></font>

220
00:12:59,384 --> 00:13:02,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So you do have a meeting!</b></font>

221
00:13:11,404 --> 00:13:13,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My heart is really beating fast!</b></font>

222
00:13:13,434 --> 00:13:16,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like just before getting on the
extreme ride at the amusement park.</b></font>

223
00:13:16,374 --> 00:13:20,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, shoot! Lucky you! I'm envious!</b></font>

224
00:13:20,274 --> 00:13:23,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think it's that much fun.</b></font>

225
00:13:23,674 --> 00:13:26,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going, Iketani.</b></font>

226
00:13:26,014 --> 00:13:29,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah! I can count on you, Takumi! Go all out!</b></font>

227
00:13:29,214 --> 00:13:31,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shoo, shoo! Get away, you guys!</b></font>

228
00:13:35,594 --> 00:13:38,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds great!</b></font>

229
00:13:38,364 --> 00:13:42,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the best! A turbo can
never sound like that!</b></font>

230
00:13:53,574 --> 00:13:56,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The first corner is coming up.</i></b></font>

231
00:13:56,714 --> 00:13:58,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll figure out what he does different from me,</i></b></font>

232
00:13:58,544 --> 00:14:01,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and then steal his technique...</i></b></font>

233
00:14:02,854 --> 00:14:04,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey...! Hey!</b></font>

234
00:14:04,524 --> 00:14:07,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! Brake!</b></font>

235
00:14:12,864 --> 00:14:15,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How... How can he control the car like this?</i></b></font>

236
00:14:15,694 --> 00:14:18,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's going on?!</i></b></font>

237
00:14:21,374 --> 00:14:23,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible...</b></font>

238
00:14:25,074 --> 00:14:27,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The speedometer warning sound is on!</i></b></font>

239
00:14:27,914 --> 00:14:32,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That means it is way over 100 km/hr.</i></b></font>

240
00:14:32,044 --> 00:14:34,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We're coming up on the next corner!</i></b></font>

241
00:15:07,684 --> 00:15:09,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is back already?</b></font>

242
00:15:09,654 --> 00:15:11,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what happened.</b></font>

243
00:15:11,184 --> 00:15:14,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's too early to return from the bottom.</b></font>

244
00:15:23,664 --> 00:15:25,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He passed out...</b></font>

245
00:15:27,234 --> 00:15:29,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

246
00:15:29,874 --> 00:15:32,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which corner was it?</b></font>

247
00:15:32,904 --> 00:15:35,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The third one...?</b></font>

248
00:15:35,114 --> 00:15:49,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Iketani Passes Out!"</b></font>

249
00:15:35,374 --> 00:15:38,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! I... I saw it!</b></font>

250
00:15:38,344 --> 00:15:41,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The agonized cry of his last
moment echoed through Mt. Akina!</b></font>

251
00:15:41,084 --> 00:15:43,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The scary downhill!</b></font>

252
00:15:43,284 --> 00:15:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani, in the third corner...</b></font>

253
00:15:48,294 --> 00:15:50,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...passed out!</b></font>

254
00:15:50,224 --> 00:15:51,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must be true...</b></font>

255
00:15:51,924 --> 00:15:55,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! Mr. Tachibana! Why are you here?!</b></font>

256
00:15:57,034 --> 00:16:00,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was curious...</b></font>

257
00:16:00,364 --> 00:16:02,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I suppose I'm not welcome...</b></font>

258
00:16:07,674 --> 00:16:10,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Take your time...</b></font>

259
00:16:10,474 --> 00:16:12,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that guy.</b></font>

260
00:16:12,344 --> 00:16:16,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nakazato of the Night Kids
has no opponent in Myogi.</b></font>

261
00:16:16,814 --> 00:16:18,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't be impressed</b></font>

262
00:16:18,324 --> 00:16:21,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by the technique of a person who drives a R32.</b></font>

263
00:16:21,024 --> 00:16:22,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just that the car is fast. That's all.</b></font>

264
00:16:22,994 --> 00:16:24,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if that's true...</b></font>

265
00:16:24,194 --> 00:16:25,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't think so, brother?</b></font>

266
00:16:25,824 --> 00:16:29,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here we go again. Keisuke hates the R32.</b></font>

267
00:16:29,694 --> 00:16:31,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But, Ryosuke...</b></font>

268
00:16:31,504 --> 00:16:35,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think it's good if
Nakazato defeats him first.</b></font>

269
00:16:35,774 --> 00:16:38,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the Night Kids beat</b></font>

270
00:16:38,074 --> 00:16:40,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the Eight-Six that we couldn't beat...</b></font>

271
00:16:40,844 --> 00:16:46,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...it may look like the Red Suns
are a notch lower than the Night Kids.</b></font>

272
00:16:46,044 --> 00:16:48,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the way rumors go...</b></font>

273
00:16:48,514 --> 00:16:52,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think that's Nakazato's plan.</b></font>

274
00:16:52,424 --> 00:16:55,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think you need to worry about it.</b></font>

275
00:16:55,024 --> 00:16:59,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is no one in the Night Kids
who can beat the Eight-Six.</b></font>

276
00:16:59,564 --> 00:17:01,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As long as it's the downhill of Akina,</b></font>

277
00:17:01,394 --> 00:17:03,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>no one can beat him.</b></font>

278
00:17:03,334 --> 00:17:07,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Only my brother can handle it.</b></font>

279
00:17:07,034 --> 00:17:12,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is fast and on a higher level.</b></font>

280
00:17:12,074 --> 00:17:14,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't get it...</b></font>

281
00:17:14,374 --> 00:17:16,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why can't the new state-of-the-art cars</b></font>

282
00:17:16,814 --> 00:17:19,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with high power beat the Eight-Six?</b></font>

283
00:17:19,984 --> 00:17:23,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sometimes a car has too much
power to do the job. That's all.</b></font>

284
00:17:23,814 --> 00:17:24,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

285
00:17:24,854 --> 00:17:28,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The turbo power is a strong
weapon on the straightaway,</b></font>

286
00:17:28,824 --> 00:17:31,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but coming out of the corner,
it hinders the car's behavior.</b></font>

287
00:17:31,924 --> 00:17:33,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like a double-edged sword.</b></font>

288
00:17:33,864 --> 00:17:36,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From that aspect...</b></font>

289
00:17:36,264 --> 00:17:39,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...once the Eight-Six is set,
it can go faster and faster.</b></font>

290
00:17:39,364 --> 00:17:41,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the technical courses
where the straights are short,</b></font>

291
00:17:41,904 --> 00:17:43,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>sometimes the car that
is aggressive can be faster,</b></font>

292
00:17:43,874 --> 00:17:45,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even though it doesn't have much power.</b></font>

293
00:17:45,674 --> 00:17:48,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's turbo, which had increased power,</b></font>

294
00:17:48,174 --> 00:17:50,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>had the opposite effect...</b></font>

295
00:17:50,944 --> 00:17:52,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right...</b></font>

296
00:17:52,414 --> 00:17:56,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the downhill of Akina,
the total amount of time I could use...</b></font>

297
00:17:56,554 --> 00:17:59,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...all of its 350 horses was very little.</b></font>

298
00:18:01,124 --> 00:18:03,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right after the moment I thought
I had pulled far away from him,</b></font>

299
00:18:03,724 --> 00:18:05,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I had to brake for the next corner,</b></font>

300
00:18:05,694 --> 00:18:08,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and the time it took before I could
accelerate was too long, and it irritated me.</b></font>

301
00:18:08,664 --> 00:18:12,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, that is what happens
with the FR that transmits power</b></font>

302
00:18:12,334 --> 00:18:14,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to the road surface using only the rear tires.</b></font>

303
00:18:14,004 --> 00:18:15,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, wait a minute!</b></font>

304
00:18:15,374 --> 00:18:18,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then what will happen
with the R32 that is a 4WD?</b></font>

305
00:18:18,544 --> 00:18:20,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The ATTESA E-TS System
can give stable traction</b></font>

306
00:18:20,644 --> 00:18:22,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even when giving it the gas,</b></font>

307
00:18:22,344 --> 00:18:23,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so he can use the turbo power</b></font>

308
00:18:23,714 --> 00:18:26,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>as much as he wants, can't he?</b></font>

309
00:18:26,244 --> 00:18:30,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nakazato's R32 may
be able to beat the Eight-Six...</b></font>

310
00:18:36,194 --> 00:18:38,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

311
00:18:38,824 --> 00:18:40,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome!</b></font>

312
00:18:46,764 --> 00:18:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Yuno Hana Manju"</b></font>

313
00:18:48,374 --> 00:18:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Pharmacy"</b></font>

314
00:18:48,374 --> 00:18:49,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Tagawa Liquor"</b></font>

315
00:18:49,434 --> 00:18:52,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I feel strange...</b></font>

316
00:18:52,674 --> 00:18:55,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The way I look at you has changed...</b></font>

317
00:18:55,414 --> 00:18:57,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that?</b></font>

318
00:18:57,774 --> 00:19:00,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Have another <i>onsen-manju</i> ["hot spring bun"].</b></font>

319
00:19:00,444 --> 00:19:01,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

320
00:19:07,054 --> 00:19:10,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you're doing that,
it's the regular Takumi.</b></font>

321
00:19:10,954 --> 00:19:14,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A spacey guy who looks
sleepy and eats <i>manju.</i></b></font>

322
00:19:14,494 --> 00:19:17,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Calling me a spacey guy is pretty rude.</b></font>

323
00:19:17,134 --> 00:19:19,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

324
00:19:19,534 --> 00:19:22,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...once you're in the
driver's seat of the Eight-Six</b></font>

325
00:19:22,174 --> 00:19:24,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and jump onto the mountain...</b></font>

326
00:19:27,674 --> 00:19:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...you are the pride of
the street racers in Akina!</b></font>

327
00:19:30,014 --> 00:19:32,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The hero everyone admires!</b></font>

328
00:19:32,184 --> 00:19:33,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

329
00:19:33,484 --> 00:19:34,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that right?</b></font>

330
00:19:34,684 --> 00:19:36,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's embarrassing...</b></font>

331
00:19:36,854 --> 00:19:39,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told you I'm not talking about now!</b></font>

332
00:19:39,184 --> 00:19:42,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now you're just a spacey
guy who is eating <i>manju.</i></b></font>

333
00:19:42,994 --> 00:19:47,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To tell you the truth, I feel kind of strange...</b></font>

334
00:19:47,224 --> 00:19:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>About what?</b></font>

335
00:19:48,694 --> 00:19:51,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>During the last race,</b></font>

336
00:19:51,404 --> 00:19:54,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and yesterday when I had Iketani ride with me,</b></font>

337
00:19:54,534 --> 00:19:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was just driving as usual.</b></font>

338
00:19:58,074 --> 00:20:02,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't understand why
everyone is so excited about it.</b></font>

339
00:20:02,914 --> 00:20:08,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never done anything that
makes other people happy.</b></font>

340
00:20:10,184 --> 00:20:12,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm starting to think...</i></b></font>

341
00:20:12,224 --> 00:20:14,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...that driving is becoming fun...</i></b></font>

342
00:20:28,404 --> 00:20:30,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey!
--What?</b></font>

343
00:20:31,804 --> 00:20:33,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A black R32?</b></font>

344
00:20:33,944 --> 00:20:36,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the one we've seen a lot recently.</b></font>

345
00:20:36,714 --> 00:20:38,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Crap! He's on my bumper!</b></font>

346
00:20:38,814 --> 00:20:41,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't let it pass us! Try hard!</b></font>

347
00:20:41,144 --> 00:20:44,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah... On the downhill,
the difference in power is smaller.</b></font>

348
00:20:44,254 --> 00:20:47,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have the Eight-Six that beat the FD!</b></font>

349
00:21:11,514 --> 00:21:13,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Small fish!</i></b></font>

350
00:21:21,724 --> 00:21:23,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He passed on the outside!</b></font>

351
00:21:32,034 --> 00:21:35,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a thrill! A completely
different level of acceleration.</b></font>

352
00:21:35,104 --> 00:21:36,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As I thought...</b></font>

353
00:21:36,404 --> 00:21:40,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...in reality, it is impossible
to race and beat a power car...</b></font>

354
00:21:40,144 --> 00:21:42,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...with a gutless car.</b></font>

355
00:21:46,484 --> 00:21:49,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is an amazing machine.</i></b></font>

356
00:21:49,614 --> 00:21:51,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Since I switched to this car,</i></b></font>

357
00:21:51,284 --> 00:21:55,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>my former rivals are no longer a match for me.</i></b></font>

358
00:21:55,824 --> 00:21:59,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I lost the opponents who</i>
<i>made me run seriously.</i></b></font>

359
00:22:00,994 --> 00:22:02,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The drift game,</i></b></font>

360
00:22:02,394 --> 00:22:05,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>which has become popular recently</i>
<i>but is just flash, is not my style.</i></b></font>

361
00:22:05,434 --> 00:22:07,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Unless it is an extreme battle,</i></b></font>

362
00:22:07,434 --> 00:22:10,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>which attacks with gripping tires</i>
<i>and makes me concentrate totally,</i></b></font>

363
00:22:10,774 --> 00:22:13,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have no use for it.</i></b></font>

364
00:22:13,044 --> 00:22:14,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Come out!</i></b></font>

365
00:22:14,444 --> 00:22:16,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Akina's Eight-Six!</i></b></font>

366
00:22:16,874 --> 00:22:19,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>At first glance, I felt it!</i></b></font>

367
00:22:19,344 --> 00:22:22,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are enough of an opponent for me.</i></b></font>

368
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

369
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sou tanin wa kaizai shinai</i></b></font>

370
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, tomaritakunai</i></b></font>

371
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Gisei ni natta ai ga cry shite mo</i></b></font>

372
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Peak mezashite, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

373
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! Keikokuon wa so cheap!</i></b></font>

374
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sheep-tachi wa michi wo akero</i></b></font>

375
00:22:57,614 --> 00:23:00,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cuz I'm never gonna stop, streak my dream</i></b></font>

376
00:23:00,054 --> 00:23:03,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Easy na motivation subete wa simulation</i></b></font>

377
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:07,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nigetemitatte doko demo safety zone</i></b></font>

378
00:23:07,994 --> 00:23:12,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nani ka wo te ni irete nani ka wo wasureteku</i></b></font>

379
00:23:12,004 --> 00:23:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekai ga kowaretemo kawaranai</i></b></font>

380
00:23:15,934 --> 00:23:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beasty shout, dare no te ni sae oenai</i></b></font>

381
00:23:24,014 --> 00:23:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hageshii yume jikan sae mo ima koeteku</i></b></font>

382
00:23:31,384 --> 00:23:35,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, yami o harisaite iku</i></b></font>

383
00:23:35,424 --> 00:23:37,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Like a streak to the peak</i></b></font>

384
00:23:37,394 --> 00:23:43,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekaijuu no kogekitta yoru o keshiteku</i></b></font>

385
00:23:43,534 --> 00:23:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, michi o hiraiteku</i></b></font>

386
00:23:47,404 --> 00:23:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Di-ding down, another round never slow down</i></b></font>

387
00:23:50,074 --> 00:23:52,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Konma zero-ichibyou de knockdown</i></b></font>

388
00:23:52,074 --> 00:23:54,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yoin nokoshikietekou to the next town</i></b></font>

389
00:23:54,274 --> 00:23:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hokori mau haishachi ni hau</i></b></font>

390
00:23:56,114 --> 00:23:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rikutsu dake no nougakitachi</i></b></font>

391
00:23:58,074 --> 00:24:00,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Jamakusai kara shikato shitekou</i></b></font>

392
00:24:00,044 --> 00:24:02,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Streaker satte yuku street no mukou</i></b></font>

393
00:24:02,184 --> 00:24:03,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something they would know</i></b></font>

394
00:24:03,384 --> 00:24:07,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, tsuzuku hatenai michi wo</i></b></font>

395
00:24:07,424 --> 00:24:11,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai mo kako mo furimukazu</i></b></font>

396
00:24:11,424 --> 00:24:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yukeru anata kagayaiteiru</i></b></font>

397
00:24:15,494 --> 00:24:20,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, ima o ikiteiru</i></b></font>

398
00:24:26,344 --> 00:24:28,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I heard about it!</i></b></font>

399
00:24:28,414 --> 00:24:31,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You were a very famous</i>
<i>street racer in Akina once.</i></b></font>

400
00:24:31,374 --> 00:24:34,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yeah. I often drove with Bunta.</i></b></font>

401
00:24:34,784 --> 00:24:39,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now in Akina, Takumi is going to have</i>
<i>to race with Nakazato of the Night Kids.</i></b></font>

402
00:24:39,784 --> 00:24:43,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yeah... But Takumi doesn't want to race.</i></b></font>

403
00:24:43,224 --> 00:24:46,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What?! Then we can't see them race!</i></b></font>

404
00:24:46,264 --> 00:24:49,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't worry. I have an idea.</i></b></font>

405
00:24:49,534 --> 00:24:51,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Leave it to me.</i></b></font>

406
00:24:51,364 --> 00:24:54,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next time on Initial D, "A Racer's Pride."</i></b></font>

407
00:24:54,634 --> 00:24:56,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

